                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Pendant ce long tourment des heures douloureuses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Accordez-lui par moi des minutes heureuses !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi je prie ayant, comme un bon ouvrier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Le désir de gagner quelque brin de laurier",
