                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Pour parer de renom ta vieillesse adorée ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Je voudrais, conquérant l'immortelle durée,",
