                    "line_text": "Poëte, quand ton souffle a pénétré mon être,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Alors que je te tiens serrée entre mes bras",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "J'oublie en un moment la haine des ingrats,",
